The beloved child Muhammad Ayman Al-Sakafi
His father is Dr. and lecturer at Al-Azhar University Ayman Al-Sakafi, who was arrested by the Israeli occupation during its invasion of Al-Awda Hospital..
This child also lost his mother months ago..

Muhammad is the only child of his father and mother, with his sisters..

Muhammad was injured a few days ago after his family was forced to flee from Tel Al-Zaatar, north of Gaza, and after they passed and were searched at the checkpoint, they were shot..

5 bullets penetrated Muhammad's frail body, and he is now fighting for his life in the intensive care unit after undergoing several operations to try to stop the bleeding..

Please pray for his recovery, and God is sufficient for us, and He is the best Disposer of affairs
